A cybersecurity company runs a password cracking challenge on a laptop, adding an interactive element. Tech companies display demo screens showing their latest apps. Human resources teams jot notes on tablets as students introduce themselves, and students use tablets at kiosks to upload resumes to the fair database. A whiteboard lists employers scheduling same-day interviews, providing further opportunities. An aroma of coffee and catered snacks spreads from the lounge, while students exit carrying tote bags and a stack of business cards.

Career counselors are assisting unsure students by redirecting them toward applicable industries and guiding them in their job search during the event. International students queue for advice on visa sponsorship requirements. Announcement chimes signal the final hour of the fair, and near the exit, a post-event survey link flashes on the monitors. As students exit, they are seen with tote bags and stacks of business cards.

A data science company features a live dashboard showcasing fair attendance, and groups of friends navigate the event map to mark their target employers. Additionally, international students are seen queuing for advice on visa sponsorship requirements.
